[OPENING THEME PLAYING]

00:12.838 --> 00:15.885
♪ SOME PEOPLE STAND
IN THE DARKNESS ♪

00:17.017 --> 00:20.150
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

00:20.890 --> 00:24.589
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED
TO HAVE SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.720 --> 00:27.505
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.158 --> 00:30.247
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:30.900 --> 00:33.816
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT ♪

00:36.993 --> 00:38.864
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

00:38.995 --> 00:42.346
